lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps wondered whether the younger generation of swimmers is ready to fill his very large shoes. The 18-time Olympic champion is finding out that, yes, the new kids are all right.

headline.print_headline: Who's New on the US Olympic Swimming Team for Rio
